            "id": 6253044,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 甲骨文(ORCL-US)大漲5.85%，報208.56美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>甲骨文(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>)截至台北時間26日22:30股價上漲11.53美元，報208.56美元，漲幅5.85%，成交量2,563,304（股），盤中最高價209.50美元、最低價208.56美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.42%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.49%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.67%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.16%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>甲骨文(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-9.67%</li> <li>近 1 月：-29.7%</li> <li>近 3 月：-15.39%</li> <li>近 6 月：+23.01%</li> <li>今年以來：+19.96%</li></ul></section></main>",
