            "id": 6253047,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 迪爾(DE-US)大跌5.08%，報472.84美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>迪爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DE-US</a>)截至台北時間26日22:32股價下跌25.29美元，報472.84美元，跌幅5.08%，成交量281,350（股），盤中最高價482.45美元、最低價472.50美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.48%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.5%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.64%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.23%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>迪爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DE-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+3.37%</li> <li>近 1 月：+3.61%</li> <li>近 3 月：+0.39%</li> <li>近 6 月：-3.89%</li> <li>今年以來：+17.13%</li></ul></section></main>",
